name: Fukumon's Little Christmas #4
description:
Fukumon finally found out what bothers him. The Christmas preparation in his house is almost completed, but something’s missing: Santa. When he’s about to go to the rooftop and looking for Santa, there he is. Apparently, Santa Claus is there the whole time, but he couldn’t get down the chimney.

“How can I get in? It’s too narrow and the fire’s on!” said Santa.

- to be continued -
